Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.71,0:00:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.18,0:00:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.72,0:00:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.83,0:00:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.04,0:00:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.84,0:00:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.12,0:01:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.56,0:01:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.23,0:01:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.87,0:01:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.57,0:01:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.88,0:01:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看见钢弹的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.61,0:01:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不可活着回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.28,0:01:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.82,0:01:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹在这里啊!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.27,0:01:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没事吧!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.07,0:01:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以…\N代替希洛出战吗…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.84,0:01:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种事…别担心那种事!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.81,0:01:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要更加担心自己的将来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.78,0:02:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十六话\N[悲哀的决战]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.09,0:02:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在在魏德尔海\N菲尔希那冰棚上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.56,0:02:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大约5分钟后到达柏克莱基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.36,0:02:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,周围有索敌反应吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷达和热源也没反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.10,0:02:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.27,0:02:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚哈特的调查队本队不会轻易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.11,0:02:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放弃追击我们，看来认为他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.41,0:02:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重整队型进行强攻比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.84,0:02:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是正确的判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.18,0:02:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ原来也有优秀的人材吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.10,0:02:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.67,0:02:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯，特洛瓦‧巴顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把他们两人带来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.31,0:03:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是杰克斯‧马吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要握手吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.92,0:03:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.62,0:03:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和以前令卫星团结起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,领导者的名字一样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.93,0:03:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真名吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.96,0:03:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的是真名吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.37,0:03:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名字对今后的我们来说\N毫无意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.57,0:03:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们尽可能准备了最好的招待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.84,0:03:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你们别客气，慢慢休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.35,0:03:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的机动战士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.06,0:03:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你高兴吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.39,0:03:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.86,0:03:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,01已经完全修理好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.20,0:03:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后只差仔细调整操纵性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:03:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.40,0:04:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是负责整备你的钢弹的米萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.00,0:04:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后只差把驾驶舱和你配合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萨虽然年轻\N但他有真材实料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何时开始?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.58,0:04:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明早好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.22,0:04:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯，在那之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没话要对杰克斯特校说吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.12,0:04:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会多谢他，用我的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.76,0:04:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀死杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.29,0:04:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是我多谢的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.56,0:04:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这场决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对为了保护卫星而战的士兵来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是短时间的障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.94,0:04:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是中途的一点吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.74,0:04:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我从未做过这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这场决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.31,0:04:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对杰克斯来说是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.92,0:04:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我觉得也不可让希洛死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经说过很多次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.96,0:04:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹01已经毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.09,0:04:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里连一个平衡器也没剩下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.16,0:04:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是真是假，希望你让我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.00,0:05:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,见过杰克斯特校后再弄清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.07,0:05:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校不在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.27,0:05:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，请你让我见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾是这里负责人的诺茵特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.60,0:05:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果说是莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.01,0:05:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她应该会见我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说过那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.68,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.15,0:05:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?做得好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.62,0:05:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.49,0:05:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下正前来这里吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.50,0:05:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然被匹斯克拉福特的情报网找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.13,0:05:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来要当被罗姆斐拉财团\N完全知道比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你们加倍小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.84,0:05:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.31,0:05:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奉承罗姆斐拉财团的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会无止境地出现吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.71,0:05:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打倒包庇钢弹的杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是对财团假装尽忠的好藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.79,0:06:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,调查队的追击或许会很厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.39,0:06:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，为何会是OZ的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯一定要被追杀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.53,0:06:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯要走的路没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.60,0:06:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，我无心偷听的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.07,0:06:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我也有我自己的答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在OZ渡过长时间的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.34,0:06:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把自己的清高美学带进战争里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分成敌我也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.72,0:06:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯一能互相认同的是精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.15,0:06:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他们不顾生死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.69,0:06:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们即使豁出性命也要战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们的生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才是士兵的真正模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.63,0:06:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我太天真!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.73,0:06:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为他们有保护卫星而战的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.64,0:06:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯你也有要保护的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.37,0:06:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没资格拥有要保护的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他们会说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.84,0:06:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这想法才天真吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.18,0:06:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不须要装作清高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果只能那样战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.45,0:07:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只会在这里被钢弹打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.46,0:07:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些事一定要豁出性命\N才能学到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.43,0:07:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵，这场决斗会拖很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我尽量不想被妨碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.17,0:07:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.94,0:07:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会尽力阻止调查队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.97,0:07:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.94,0:07:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我担心的是\N匹斯克拉福特家的重要人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.27,0:07:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,近卫兵大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.61,0:07:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不\N莉莉娜殿下才是你重要的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.08,0:07:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保护那孩子能令你专心地战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.16,0:07:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不相信我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.19,0:07:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想别人碰我的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.33,0:07:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.03,0:07:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它没有接上自爆装置的回路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.93,0:07:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校说没必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.77,0:07:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为上次一役令他后悔了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.51,0:08:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他今次好像想干到底啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用你的机动战士战斗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是让我用你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.09,0:08:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.89,0:08:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这么过于施舍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗触觉会变得迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有你是那样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.89,0:08:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我指的是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.43,0:08:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好坚强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗，并非用01
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是用03决斗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们究竟在想什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被他认为我过于施舍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.65,0:08:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我的心情也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校，要把托尔吉斯的左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回复原状吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.15,0:08:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在还能从01拆下必要的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用，这样就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.92,0:08:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.73,0:08:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是西伯利亚决战的延续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.80,0:08:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时候，托尔吉斯被击毁左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.10,0:09:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当是理所当然的不利条件就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.00,0:09:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是技师和驾驶员的分别呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.24,0:09:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，我们做幕后的事就够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.41,0:09:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这或许叫幕前的尊严啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.85,0:09:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，这是我天真的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么时候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2时32分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后的交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.94,0:09:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.19,0:09:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这重量会令他的左手很辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.92,0:11:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，刚刚开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.26,0:11:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有雷达反应!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.57,0:11:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.58,0:11:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用雪消除热源吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.92,0:12:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不会死在这点战斗里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.80,0:12:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗开始后已过了大约3小时!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.80,0:12:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无竟义的战斗却持续了很久啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无意义?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说无意义!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.61,0:12:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对吗?虽然我不知详情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.81,0:12:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但这基地的人正被OZ追杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.34,0:12:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥有相同敌人的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.98,0:12:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这种偏僻地方决斗有何意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.18,0:12:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶员间的恩怨，真无聊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.15,0:12:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.09,0:12:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，之前还互相仇杀的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.99,0:12:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没恩怨才古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.16,0:12:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在感到战斗无意义前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.83,0:13:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这场决斗不会停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.03,0:13:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在时代里再次找寻自我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.17,0:13:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是士兵的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,需要敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.64,0:13:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，若能找到要保护的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,士兵就会重生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.38,0:13:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也须要时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.75,0:13:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们现在失去保护卫星的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.05,0:13:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以在这种地方浪费时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了让决斗快点完结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.72,0:13:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去准备以免第三者介入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.06,0:13:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你指调查队吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.03,0:13:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦!你怎样战斗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要希洛报恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.85,0:13:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没子弹后就按那个钮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.52,0:13:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左手会较轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.23,0:14:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样一来，你已经没有武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.24,0:14:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光剑吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦也很为我费心神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.64,0:14:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要那样才行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.23,0:14:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁也会为过去\N所犯的错误而痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.67,0:14:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，你们不年轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.64,0:14:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你们想着创造未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.21,0:14:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们一族能和你们见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.25,0:14:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实感光荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.99,0:15:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,民航机!马上着陆!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是作战空域!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帕根，快点，不可停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.99,0:15:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但这是追杀杰克斯‧马吉斯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.43,0:15:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,调查队侦察机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.83,0:15:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道他们会做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.13,0:15:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们不会追到柏克莱基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.27,0:15:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听天由命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,民航机没减速度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.57,0:15:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上击落它!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是钢弹!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.22,0:15:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在前面决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.52,0:15:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.26,0:15:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要制止他和杰克斯的决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.43,0:15:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这场决斗无意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.56,0:15:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了，你快点去比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.33,0:15:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,调查队的行动看来很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.45,0:16:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的左手不灵活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.45,0:16:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发觉了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.02,0:16:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你蓄意留下弱点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.06,0:16:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙太多事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想把这种美学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这场决斗里发挥出来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.54,0:16:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.68,0:16:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.28,0:16:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.85,0:16:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，有信寄给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.22,0:16:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别挡住!走开!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我不会走开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.02,0:16:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这封信指示了\N你今后的生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.06,0:16:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有义务读这封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.13,0:16:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是杰克斯‧马吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主，请你离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.34,0:17:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要为部下报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.44,0:17:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.68,0:17:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就以匹斯克拉福特之名命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.28,0:17:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你现在马上停止这场决斗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.05,0:17:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坚强了啊，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.12,0:17:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才是匹斯克拉福特的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就用那双眼看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.46,0:17:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗有多污秽!有多卑鄙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.73,0:17:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真过份!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.80,0:17:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是匹斯克拉福特的骑士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.84,0:17:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他没理由能做出那么卑鄙的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.68,0:17:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐，诺茵特尉来电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.05,0:17:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我误会了你是个更真诚的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.22,0:17:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟然能冷眼旁观这种战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.22,0:17:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是比赛也不是决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.82,0:17:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这只是自相残杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.79,0:17:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.46,0:17:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被你鄙视也没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.83,0:18:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我相信杰克斯特校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.80,0:18:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会出言反对他想做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.04,0:18:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!打倒杰克斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.37,0:18:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,属于OZ这等卑劣组织的人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.34,0:18:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是山克王国的耻辱!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.18,0:18:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧!杀死他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.21,0:18:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!莉莉娜殿下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.05,0:18:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.85,0:18:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾和OZ一起行动的确是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.22,0:18:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我们不会否定犯下的那过错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不能找藉口说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.50,0:18:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们爱山克王国才选择那条路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.83,0:18:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么命运的安排也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.50,0:18:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望自己哥哥身亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.37,0:18:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这等不经大脑的想法，请你停止!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.74,0:18:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.81,0:18:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的王兄!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.28,0:18:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前，由匹斯克拉福特家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.68,0:18:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被联合军灭亡那时开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.18,0:18:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他发誓要报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.69,0:18:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集结山克王国\N四散的力量很困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.79,0:19:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了接近联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.33,0:19:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他加入OZ，等候时机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.16,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戴起杰克斯‧马吉斯的面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.03,0:19:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这双手已经沾满太多鲜血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.37,0:19:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜才配复兴山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.08,0:19:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在OZ于世界产生新混乱的现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.98,0:19:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯失去了\N自己存在的意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯有在和钢弹的战斗里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.98,0:19:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他才能找到身为士兵的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那样的战斗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.76,0:19:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想拥有和随心而活的希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.09,0:19:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能对等战斗的精神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了能率直地爱护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.06,0:19:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国和匹斯克拉福特之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.60,0:19:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他决定失去性命也不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.01,0:19:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会继续相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.81,0:19:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想追随杰克斯想做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.21,0:19:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想陪他\N找寻他想找的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.08,0:19:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你喜欢我哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.62,0:20:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，我爱他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.85,0:20:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你永远保护我哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知能否做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.03,0:20:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为杰克斯特校很任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.73,0:20:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是匹斯克拉福特的血呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多大型运输机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.63,0:20:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从3时方向接近中!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕是调查队的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.97,0:20:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,数目呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.97,0:20:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能确认的也已超过30部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是大型部队!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.34,0:20:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出动所有能使用的机动战士!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎击调查队!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.32,0:20:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到吗?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有你，杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有30部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.33,0:20:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包括艾亚利兹也只有100部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.39,0:20:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每人30部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.00,0:20:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能轻松击落它们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.87,0:20:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不!等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.33,0:20:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去引开他们!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.04,0:20:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光荣归于卫星!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.31,0:20:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!后会有期!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.81,0:21:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了决一胜负啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.45,0:21:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后也会是个难应付的对手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.63,0:21:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.97,0:21:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的艾亚利兹部队\N已经准备好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.64,0:21:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么\N你和莉莉娜一起离开那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.74,0:21:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.34,0:21:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们一逃离那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.21,0:21:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就会向调查队投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.28,0:21:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我也能战斗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.35,0:21:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.78,0:21:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要保护未来山克王国的重要人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.82,0:21:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不!让我保护她!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.46,0:21:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.03,0:21:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯，你要平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.61,0:22:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以什么形式也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.41,0:22:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种战斗结束了真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.82,0:22:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.60,0:22:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.60,0:22:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.60,0:22:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.60,0:22:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.10,0:22:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那个惹人厌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.60,0:23:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因为心理有爱意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.10,0:23:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是让人挂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.60,0:23:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我不该说出强人所难的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.60,0:23:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.69,0:23:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回预告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.40,0:23:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战火继续扩展至宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.57,0:23:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.77,0:23:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在击败联合军余党的同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.10,0:23:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行了介入卫星的策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.77,0:23:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔和迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.04,0:23:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了公开OZ的阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.61,0:23:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决定前去宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.71,0:23:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，本应是故乡的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.21,0:23:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却宣布钢弹是敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.28,0:23:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新机动战记-钢弹W，第十七话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.42,0:23:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背叛的遥远故乡

